There are both theoretical concepts and practical considerations to be taken into account. 
Some of the major points for discussion are:
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ the role of DCs and warehouses;
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ distribution cost factors and relationships;
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ a methodology for planning a physical distribution structure;
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ an overview of different modelling techniques;
