mediationÃ¢â‚¬â„¢. In order to counter the threat from Ã¢â‚¬Ëœpure-playÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ internet retailers, and to offer a 
greater choice of channels to consumers, the Ã¢â‚¬Ëœbricks-and-mortarÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ retailers also entered the internet selling channel, necessitating multichannel fulfilment.
