In general, the greatest benefits are to be found with the improvement in the first two of these Ã¢â‚¬â€œ speedier replenishment and better store assortment. Overall, benefits can be found in both 
cost reduction and service improvement. Some of the key factors and their associated benefits 
can be summarized as:
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Automated systems that reduce labour and administrative costs.
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Sharing information, which leads to more timely deliveries and falling inventory levels 
