 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Cross-docking, which reduces inventory levels at the DC.
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Concentrating on fewer suppliers, which reduces transaction and administration costs.
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Offering the right products to the right customers, which increases volume sales and economies of scale.
 Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ More timely, more accurate information, which means that customer needs are more 
