dispatch area and are then loaded on to outbound vehicles for onward dispatch to the 
next Ã¢â‚¬ËœnodeÃ¢â‚¬â„¢ in the supply chain (eg to a trans-shipment depot or to a freight forwarderÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s depot for groupage/consolidation).
